Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}動不了？ 還是不想動？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}將孤獨轉化為強悍！
